{"tid":1088291,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想換SSD, 好多問題想問下各位巴打","createTime":"2019-04-02T02:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T07:25:46.000Z","uid":76960,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fabbf34516c63a5ff97e1b6281c2abf2c5287e","tid":1088291,"uid":76960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"小弟尋晚一隻用黎裝WINDOWS既3.5 HDD死左..<br />\n把心一橫想換SSD黎做裝WINDOWS既HDD<br />\n因為之前都冇用過SSD既關係, 所以上網查左一輪資料, 發現如果都有分好多種SSD, <br />\n咁我見到一種叫做M.2 NVME 既SSD, 話速度上比傳統既SSD 可以快5倍, 而且價錢唔係差太遠, 於是就想買呢一款SSD<br />\n見到好多人都提及一定要CHECK下自己既底版支唔支援呢種SSD<br />\n小弟就係用以下呢塊版:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gigabyte.com/hk/Motherboard/GA-B150M-D3H-rev-10#ov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gigabyte.com%2Fhk%2FMotherboard%2FGA-B150M-D3H-rev-10%23ov&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=95ab877d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gigabyte.com/hk/Motherboard/GA-B150M-D3H-rev-10#ov</a><br />\n見到入面有寫住 &quot;高速PCIe Gen3 x4 M.2插槽設計，提供最高達32Gb/s資料傳輸頻寬 (同時支援PCIe NVMe或 SATA固態硬碟)&quot;<br />\n係咪代表我底版係可以裝到呢?<br />\n<br />\n另一個問題就係.. 如果想用呢個SSD黎裝WINDOWS 10<br />\n係唔係我有實體碟, 就只需要好似平時裝WINDOWS 咁, 將BOOT DRIVE 改做CD-ROM, 之後RUN碟入安裝介面就可以簡到果隻SSD黎裝, 定係用呢一款SSD 安裝WINDOWS 既程序係麻煩D 同平時唔同既呢??<br />\n<br />\n唔該咁多位巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d555de4ea76ba7cc0913bad76b242c6c5eb47c6","tid":1088291,"uid":62527,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n係"},{"pid":"43198dc7ffc6b378e84aed9147f3663afb51bddf","tid":1088291,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n係"},{"pid":"0f0371b94d80caecc5bc36d8aa6620cb4fbead2f","tid":1088291,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"係，係"},{"pid":"495e5d19d68df3ca6de5e09509ae8361495808e0","tid":1088291,"uid":14